description: This common Anurak purrs with a rating of 36, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 72, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 1 for East, Nine Lives for South, and 5 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [72 Votes, Common]
